l, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. William Newdigate was born in 1313, in Newdigate, Surrey, England, United Kingdom. She married William Newdigate in 1332, in Newdigate, Surrey, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1313–":"1313–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1333–Female":"1333–Surnud","1313–Female":"1313–Surnud","1313":"1313","1333":"1333","1332":"1332","Newdigate, Mole Valley, Surrey, England":"Newdigate, Surrey, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1313–":"1313–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1333–Female":"1333–Kuollut","1313–Female":"1313–Kuollut","1313":"1313","1333":"1333","1332":"1332","Newdigate, Mole Valley, Surrey, England":"Newdigate, Surrey, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1313–":"1313–Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1333–Female":"1333–Décédée","1313–Female":"1313–Décédée","1313":"1313","1333":"1333","1332":"1332","Newdigate, Mole Valley, Surrey, England":"Newdigate, Surrey, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. William Newdigate est née en 1313, à Newdigate, Surrey, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé William Newdigate en 1332, à Newdigate, Surrey, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1313–":"1313–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1333–Female":"1333–Verstorben","1313–Female":"1313–Verstorben","1313":"1313","1333":"1333","1332":"1332","Newdigate, Mole Valley, Surrey, England":"Newdigate, Surrey, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs. William Newdigate wurde 1313 in Newdigate, Surrey, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hat 1332 in Newdigate, Surrey, England, United Kingdom William Newdigate geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1313–":"1313–Desede","–Male":"Desede","1333–Female":"1333–Desede","1313–Female":"1313–Desede","1313":"1313","1333":"1333","1332":"1332","